Do you know how often we try new things on our clients! 

✨troubleshooting new ideas for retention

✨ trying new techniques and styles we’ve learned in trainings 

✨trying new products or mapping techniques 

Im lucky enough to have been experimenting with @claire__liberty for 4 years now. It hasn’t always been perfect but we’ve always communicated desired outcomes and made sure to stay on the same page. 

So here is a set we’ve been perfecting for a couple months - the Angel Set. 

🤷🏼‍♀️ what is it? 

While Claire naps - I place an unfanned bundle of mega volume 0.03mm lash extensions on each individual lash.

 This makes the wispy / textured / wet look

  That is ✨ The Angel Set ✨
